01:03:22.120 --> 01:03:25.120
And without the brake, it cannot stop.

01:03:25.120 --> 01:03:32.120
And so it's the question, as Sabine mentioned, of the balance between those two parts.

01:03:32.120 --> 01:03:38.120
Which are meant to be. One, the brake, and the other one, the accelerator.

01:03:38.120 --> 01:03:49.120
And as a man, I have to say that I really appreciate that my wife has got this soothing power to cool down.

01:03:49.120 --> 01:03:53.120
And as we know that, especially in Austria, we had some time.

01:03:53.120 --> 01:04:02.120
When Shri Mataji said that the Austrian ladies have a tendency to take the role of the accelerator.

01:04:02.120 --> 01:04:12.120
Which creates an atmosphere which is too much on the right, which gets too hot.

01:04:12.120 --> 01:04:18.120
So I find it's very important that as a man, we support our wives.

01:04:18.120 --> 01:04:23.120
Which they fulfill the role of somebody who is soothing.

01:04:23.120 --> 01:04:25.120
Because the soothing power is silent.

01:04:25.120 --> 01:04:28.120
The soothing power doesn't show off so much.

01:04:28.120 --> 01:04:32.120
And that's why many times we don't see it.

01:04:32.120 --> 01:04:40.120
And if we can express also that we appreciate this soothing power which comes from our will.

01:04:40.120 --> 01:04:47.120
Then they might much less feel that they should do something else.

01:04:47.120 --> 01:04:49.120
This was the one thing which I wanted to say.

01:04:49.120 --> 01:04:53.120
The other thing was actually a question which would be an answer also.

01:04:53.120 --> 01:05:00.120
